{"tid":712162,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：太古Plat du jour","createTime":"2018-06-22T02:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T15:27:20.000Z","uid":181719,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"20f2864cc8e746288e502c58b9eff3d8c8f188f1","tid":712162,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:02:44.000Z","msg":"每個月食餐貴野（對我黎講啫），去咗呢間法國菜，貪佢啲菜式睇落好似比較特別，但其實法國菜係咪真係食呢啲，我係冇乜研究的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/095828_5087b6d23a8033c3b90bde9d15c50f41.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F095828_5087b6d23a8033c3b90bde9d15c50f41.jpeg&h=c1dbb028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗌咗2個set，其中一個包甜品（即係2+3courses），第一個頭盤係蒜蓉牛油焗田螺配法包，咁樣整，惹味係基本要求啦，田螺肉比較腍，唔夠彈牙，反而將蒜蓉搽上麵包度食仲好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/095855_559bef92b169cdb2a6368d54ddd4331e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F095855_559bef92b169cdb2a6368d54ddd4331e.jpeg&h=d785a09e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/095855_54f0ca47c687b79d9f49e7dc87c3a9ad.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F095855_54f0ca47c687b79d9f49e7dc87c3a9ad.jpeg&h=b64b8fa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/095856_1281e6f6456ba5958cff633a8fdd4399.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F095856_1281e6f6456ba5958cff633a8fdd4399.jpeg&h=dd73881c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一個頭盤係煎北海道帶子配煙肉青豆汁。同田螺一樣，主角一般但個汁好食，可能因為啱啱食完蒜蓉，感覺佢味道淡咗啲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/095907_884b998e6f9ec1ce846f6fd1654e094d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F095907_884b998e6f9ec1ce846f6fd1654e094d.jpeg&h=1169baa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主菜係烤羊臀肉配薯蓉&middot;迷迭香汁，點菜嘅時候，淨係睇到個名都覺得羶，就專登嗌黎試吓，一食果然非同凡響。羊肉，仲要臀肉，真係好重口味，所以如果太多羊肉味，迷迭香就冇訂企啦，完全食唔到個汁喺邊度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/095926_a7c3d9adf07b339ffe76ee59c7909f97.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F095926_a7c3d9adf07b339ffe76ee59c7909f97.jpeg&h=ccd4b87c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/095926_bcc3e0ac60f17f0536ca6b4fc056e5ca.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F095926_bcc3e0ac60f17f0536ca6b4fc056e5ca.jpeg&h=0d160ef3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一個主菜係厚切豬扒配蘋果白蘭地汁，上面果堆菜絲係有個名堂嘅，但味道唔特別，所以只係記得佢係堆菜絲。豬扒本身肉味幾濃，比起個羊臀，豬肉嘅味道真係中庸之道黎，但係個汁都係偏淡，只有小小蘋果味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/095942_a7f97c8f0d69150645965078844dea7f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F095942_a7f97c8f0d69150645965078844dea7f.jpeg&h=161cf16d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/095942_76c2dcaf13d31aacc534b565550cba75.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F095942_76c2dcaf13d31aacc534b565550cba75.jpeg&h=fc351f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後甜品要咗心太軟配雪糕，呢個出色！心太軟個殼夠滑，唔會好似溝餅碎咁樣食落鞋口，軟心唔太甜，唔漏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至於上面插住枝蠟燭，口感唔清楚，但個火唔吹唔熄，一吹就熄，都值得一讚。其實卜檯嘅時候有講係紀念日慶祝，所以佢個甜品連蠟燭上，算幾貼心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/095959_dfdbf44f5a3fe32cd8082ee1b08b19e6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F095959_dfdbf44f5a3fe32cd8082ee1b08b19e6.jpeg&h=299b4991&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f0b5dc2bc1ddea4732b6a85f43b103e309c9ef8","tid":712162,"uid":71748,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:08:37.000Z","msg":"換左部電話佢啦<br />\n影到咁都唔會想去食"},{"pid":"4fcf0d646cd9b49cf6889c727c9f550849809901","tid":712162,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f0b5dc2bc1ddea4732b6a85f43b103e309c9ef8","tid":712162,"uid":71748,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:08:37.000Z","msg":"換左部電話佢啦<br />\n影到咁都唔會想去食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:20:47.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打用部電話黎幫我兜<br />\n其實係我影相廢啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbba1465f145f45a5f2f6b0563c260f4a8e9025","tid":712162,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:33:39.000Z","msg":"比埋評分啦好嘛"},{"pid":"1cfbce2571b989d56995ba6a2be9aaf7fd8cf9d9","tid":712162,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"屌你食評冇價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93d87b497e85f8fa77897196322744c9a57f76a","tid":712162,"uid":170979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fcf0d646cd9b49cf6889c727c9f550849809901","tid":712162,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f0b5dc2bc1ddea4732b6a85f43b103e309c9ef8","tid":712162,"uid":71748,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:08:37.000Z","msg":"換左部電話佢啦<br />\n影到咁都唔會想去食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T02:20:47.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打用部電話黎幫我兜<br />\n其實係我影相廢啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-